Validate header and all components
1. Logo
2. Chat 
3. Contact us
4. Account
    a.) Account >Signin
    b.) Account > Create Account
5. Search Text Box
6. Mega Menu

Validate footer and all components
1. Register your Product section
2. Social Icons
   a.) Facebook
   b.) Twitter
   c.) Pinterest
   d.) YouTube
3. SERVICE & SUPPORT 
4. PRODUCTS
5. ACCESSORIES & OTHER
6. MAYTAG
Search Product by entering the Product Name in Search Field in Home Page and verify the search result
Verify that on Search result there is 2 section one for products and 1 for content basis documents.
Search Product by entering the Model Number in Search Field in Home Page and verify the search result which should be PDP having the searched model.
Verify sorting and filters are working fine on search result page
Verify that user able to change the Search PLP view from List view to Grid View or vice versa
Verify that searched result product contains  MSRP, Energy Guide, Review selection and Save product functionality.
Verify that refine section attributes should change when user click on Content Basis Tab
Verify the PLP page by browsing the product from navigation, Like Washers & Dryers-> Washers ->Top-Load Washers
Verify the PLP page by browsing the product from navigation, Like Washers & Dryers-> Washers ->Top-Load Washers
Verify sorting and filters are working fine on PLP page
Verify that user able to change the PLP view from List view to Grid View or vice versa
Verify that PLP product contains  MSRP, Energy Guide, Review selection and Save product functionality.
verify that user able to compare maximum 5 products by selecting compare checkboxes

Verify the following product attribute in PDP
1) Product Name
2) Review Section
3) Product Price
4) Product Description
5) Color 
6) Size
7) Image
8) Alt Image
9) Image zoom in and full screen section

Verify that following functionality is available on PDP
1) Where to Buy
2) Compare checkbox
3) Save in option for registered user & Sign in to save for guest
4)Share icon for social sharing of the product on social sites.
Verify that on clicking where to buy user redirect to Find a Store page and able to find the product by entering City,state or ZIP code.

Verify that following section is available on PDP
1) Features
2) Specs & Manuals
3) Ratings & Reviews
4) Recommendations
Verify that on clicking Rating  user able to view the ratings given by the other users for this maschine
Verify that on clicking write a review user able to write his/her review on the popup invokes after clicking on write a review
Verify that Specifications & Manuals is available on PDP
